2 possible cases of hepatitis in children identified in Oakland County, Detroit
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Michigan health officials have identified 2 possible cases of hepatitis in children. The 2 cases are in Oakland County and Detroit, they said.

The 2 patients under investigation in Michigan meet the CDC's inclusion criteria, according to the Michigan Department of Health and Human Services.

[Byline: Derick Hutchinson]

